OL,5, Violence and abuse against shop workers
OL,6, rose to 1,300 incidents a day last     
OL,7, year, a leading trade body said.       
OL,9,FIncidents against staff were up by 50% 
OL,10,Fin the year to September 2023, up from 
OL,11,F870 incidents a day the year before.   
OL,13,FThe British Retail Consortium (BRC)    
OL,14,Fcriticised the "woefully inadequate"   
OL,15,Faction taken by the government to      
OL,16,Faddress the "crisis".                  
